{"product_id":"madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA DETOX Ultra Purifying MUD mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eClarify, rejuvenate and recharge the skin with this deep-purifying detox mask. Formulated with Nordic forest lake mud, this mask ensures multiple skincare benefits: it purifies the complexion, tightens pores and conditions, absorbs excess oils, reduces outbreaks, detoxifies the skin, eliminates traces of acne and minor inflammation and helps to retain skin’s hydration. Leaves the skin feeling clean, fresh, revitalized.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e \u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​\u003c\/span\u003eRecommended to use twice a week as clarifying treatment for oily, combination skin, skin with enlarged pores, blemishes, acne. Once a week to combat skin dullness, tiredness and occasional inflammation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Kaolin, Glycerin, Montmorillonite, Diatomaceous Earth, Butylene Glycol, Aqua, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Propanediol, Lactic Acid, Sodium anisate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Charcoal Powder, Alchemilla Vulgaris (Lady's Mantle) Extract, Algae (Algae) Extract, Nasturtium Officinale (Watercress) Flower\/Leaf Extract, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 75810 (Chlorophyll), Rhamnose, Maltodextrin, Glucose, Glucuronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e16% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916409999687,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml-293845.jpg?v=1739897183","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}